===Adverb===
'''though'''

# [[despite|Despite]] that; [[however]].
#: ''I will do it, '''though'''.''
# Used to intensify statements or questions; [[indeed]].
#: ''"God, it's hot in here." — "Isn't it, '''though'''?"''

